# Results directory placeholder
#
# Experiment runs write their output here in subdirectories named
# {experiment-id}-{YYYY-MM-DD}/. Each subdirectory contains:
#
#   - metadata.txt         — run metadata (Claude Code version, hashes, etc.)
#   - baseline/            — transcripts and verdicts for baseline condition
#   - invariant-loaded/    — transcripts and verdicts for invariant-loaded condition
#   - summary.md           — human-readable summary with hypothesis verdict
#
# See test/experiments/README.md and test/experiments/run.sh for the runner
# contract, and docs/architecture/proposals/PROPOSAL-001-spec/experiments/
# for the full pre-registration methodology.
#
# Commit results after running: git add test/experiments/results/
